    <briefdescription>
<para>ContentLookupSubsystem. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Routes a GameplayTag to a DataTable based on RootTag prefix matching.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Uses the tag leaf (last segment after &apos;.&apos;) as the DataTable RowName by default.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>Example: Unlocks.Ships.Sammy RootTag: Unlocks.Ships -&gt; DT_Unlocks_Ships Leaf: Sammy -&gt; RowName &apos;Sammy&apos; </para>
    </detaileddescription>
